{"title":"雪地脚印  保岱公社纪事","authors":["王芜"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":2,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪地脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保岱公社纪事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王芜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是腊月三九天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪纷飞北风寒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记风雪深山去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一早翻过几重山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边远小村靠山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板桥上面新脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房脊顶上炊烟升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里村外分外静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽闻书记到了村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"户户出来迎亲人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快进屋里喝杯茶！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快上炕来谈谈心！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进唐家看一看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗户糊得严不严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进李家瞧一瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炕头烧得暖不暖？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝尝饭菜香不香？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸孩手凉不凉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问了这桩问那件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桩桩件件记心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记要走留不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目送书记行路远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪上脚印深变浅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临黑又过两重山。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}